@Deprecated public class BapiRequestResult extends AbstractRemoteFunctionRequestResult<BapiRequest,BapiRequestResult>
Deprecated.
This module will be discontinued, along with its classes and methods.
Class representing the result of a BAPI call returned by BapiRequest.

Use the methods AbstractRemoteFunctionRequestResult.get(String), AbstractRemoteFunctionRequestResult.get(int), AbstractRemoteFunctionRequestResult.getIfPresent(String), AbstractRemoteFunctionRequestResult.collect(String), AbstractRemoteFunctionRequestResult.size(), AbstractRemoteFunctionRequestResult.isEmpty(), or AbstractRemoteFunctionRequestResult.has(String) to access the content of the BapiRequestResult.

Use the methods AbstractRemoteFunctionRequestResult.hasFailed(), AbstractRemoteFunctionRequestResult.hasSuccessMessages(), AbstractRemoteFunctionRequestResult.hasInformationMessages(), AbstractRemoteFunctionRequestResult.hasWarningMessages(), or AbstractRemoteFunctionRequestResult.hasErrorMessages() to inspect the resulting messages from the BAPI call.
